{"tid":86083,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"關於購買M.2 SSD謎思, 集思廣益","createTime":"2017-01-18T19:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T13:21:30.000Z","uid":70467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d3a3aae3fcfb269968e528452abd0123fec742e","tid":86083,"uid":70467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T19:44:10.000Z","msg":"先多謝各位巴打抽空入黎呢個post<br />\n<br />\n事源我本身電腦用緊<span style=\"color: orange;\">SSD intel 730(480GB)</span><br />\n最近考慮緊想加SSD<br />\n咁岩見有<span style=\"color: orange;\">Intel 600p M.2 SSD(256GB)</span><br />\n對呢件野幾有興趣<br />\n(新買既SSD主要用途99%會係放GAME入去作打機之用)<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦, 大家覺得我買呢隻M.2 係唔係會比<br />\n買SATA SSD(例如加多隻intel 730)更好?<br />\n<br />\n以前一直聽開 M.2 係會比SATA SSD快好多<br />\n但做做下research見到呢個網既評測, 都令我突然有D猶疑:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">神器or廢柴？對比測試Intel 600p與東芝Q200EX</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/digital/qr8lgg.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fdigital%2Fqr8lgg.html&d=MFJV4HSU9Pby1IFF45jfp2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=cf6c4665\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/digital/qr8lgg.html</a><br />\n<br />\n不過畢竟唔係對比我依家用緊既model,<br />\n我都唔太確定上面既資料可以有幾大既參考價值<br />\n<br />\n所以想各位都畀D意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nM.2 SSD 係唔係性價比高?<br />\n另外如果買返黎會唔會有D要注意既地方呢?(例如安裝上: 4K對齊?)<br />\n<br />\n有勞各位! 感激不盡!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54bedcf6f6981a1e01e10358f7fa366d9c87c6a","tid":86083,"uid":70467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T04:23:51.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ab9a575b2e99ee0d434e65681a052537dfb2a3","tid":86083,"uid":70467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"輕輕二推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c45cd7351a29de620bd2837860b566786cd109e","tid":86083,"uid":60099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"用緊 Intel 600p M.2 SSD(256GB)<br />\n冇咩問題..又快D.. 幾抵玩~!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a90e6755f0d2491e0014318b6dd962619dda97","tid":86083,"uid":30821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"打咁多字點解唔自己google下呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf83db1b27f2d97cb49568e4656dd97f5d7a56f","tid":86083,"uid":15319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:01:36.000Z","msg":"貪佢慳位唔洗插線多D"},{"pid":"bd845c2f69129eae0192110c820b1472b669cf92","tid":86083,"uid":70467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:07:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打咁多字點解唔自己google下呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想同你地傾下計丫麻 衰鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebb19b21a2ab8bdd1ed93561d52271915ffe6eb","tid":86083,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:12:31.000Z","msg":"其實m.2係點玩法<br />\n聽得多 未玩過"},{"pid":"1ba889e84a3c1c31f4fb547d75c3fd2be62e04a7","tid":86083,"uid":707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:23:26.000Z","msg":"係好快但打機同一般ssd感謝唔到個速度<br />\n因為game要read既野好細"},{"pid":"d8b764102d3b24f4cad0380444ae5c7fcb0938e0","tid":86083,"uid":707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:23:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係好快但打機同一般ssd唔差太遠感覺唔到個速度<br />\n因為game要read既野好細</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2dcb67cdc81edf1cbefd6f93fc71d4f59e1610b4","tid":86083,"uid":33267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:25:17.000Z","msg":"馬雲 sm961 + pci-e card<br />\n無得輸"},{"pid":"3be469279b80d60d93ff73009a242b340609c3f5","tid":86083,"uid":70467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim