果隻, 但要留要你塊底板可唔可以令佢行盡個速度...我買咗H110晶片底板...係PCIE2.0x3...但隻SSD 係行到PCIE3.0x4.........不過我對比過個READ 係10XXMB/S VS 13XXMB/S 睇人地測試...所以唔太感覺到差幾遠</blockquote><br />\nM.2 要睇PCIE嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係睇M.2 slot support到咩type <br />\n<br />\n利申;新手</blockquote><br />\n有分<br />\n仲有分sata m2定nvme m2<br />\n600p係nvme m2</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依加用緊依塊 都想加張600p<br />\n巴打幫手睇下食唔食得full speed <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gigabyte.com/products/product-page.aspx?pid=4953#sp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gigabyte.com%2Fproducts%2Fproduct-page.aspx%3Fpid%3D4953%23sp&d=MFJV4HSU9Pby1IFF45jfp2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ab794cc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gigabyte.com/products/product-page.aspx?pid=4953#sp</a>"},{"pid":"7f868a851da0694f1062138970e87521676ce257","tid":86083,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T23:56:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nM.2 要睇PCIE嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係睇M.2 slot support到咩type <br />\n<br />\n利申;新手</blockquote><br />\n有分<br />\n仲有分sata m2定nvme m2<br />\n600p係nvme m2</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依加用緊依塊 都想加張600p<br />\n巴打幫手睇下食唔食得full speed <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gigabyte.com/products/product-page.aspx?pid=4953#sp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gigabyte.com%2Fproducts%2Fproduct-page.aspx%3Fpid%3D4953%23sp&d=MFJV4HSU9Pby1IFF45jfp2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ab794cc9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gigabyte.com/products/product-page.aspx?pid=4953#sp</a></blockquote><br />\n用到nvme m2<br />\n不過冇講行pcie幾，要查下<br />\n600p唔係唔好，只係爆左SLC cache就要等清cache先可以再寫入，冇direct to TLC"}]}